# 🌐 Flask Routing Assignment

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.x-blue) ![Flask](https://img.shields.io/badge/Flask-2.x-lightgrey) ![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Running-brightgreen)

A beginner Flask web server demonstrating URL routing, dynamic parameters, and error handling.

---

